Hey there,

first of all: I'm using version 2.18.3
Everything works fine, except for when I have two tables in two different tabs. I've read in the FAQ and the requests here, this issue is well-known .. but I can't figure out how to get it to work on my page. :( Tried for hours now.. and getting really desperate.

HTML for the tabs:
```
<div class="tabs">
