Anyone knows how I can get it to work? When I erase the "$.tablesorter.themes.bootstrap = { .. }"-part, the zebra widget works on both tabs/tables... but the bootstrap theme won't be applied to them. 

Your help is so much appreciated here..
Thanks in advance!

